  <WebPartDescription>
    <![CDATA[Approves subscriptions to forums or forum posts with double opt-in enabled and displays a confirmation message. Subscribers are typically directed to the page containing this web part through a link in the double opt-in activation e-mail.]]>
  </WebPartDescription>
  <WebPartDisplayName>Forum subscription confirmation</WebPartDisplayName>
