          <defaultvalue>Your subscription was confirmed successfully.</defaultvalue>
          <fieldcaption>Successful confirmation text</fieldcaption>
          <fielddescription>
            <![CDATA[Text to be displayed when a subscription was successfully confirmed.]]>
